app.name: Salad CLI+ Config Generator
home.topic:
The CLI+ Configurator was made to configure the CLI+ application easily on the internet without having to touch the config.json.

Support the Configurator!
If you want to support us consider these links

At Fanatical.com
At G2A
On Salad.io by using the referral code: 2JWUZD!

This application is an fork off ASF-WebconfigGenerator to check the fork please go here
schema.auth: We the developers of CLI+ or this web configurator can not see your token. The token is used to get basic information to the app.
schema.nicehash: Enter your Nicehash wallet and rig id like this: wallet.rigid
schema.ethermine: Enter your Ethermine wallet and rig id like this: wallet.rigid
